><div class="t m2d7 x1e h69 y682 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our profession&quot; or &quot;confession&quot;â€”</div><div class="t m1c2 x1e h69 y1bf6 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that is, our religion. There can be </div><div class="t m23b x1e h69 yc20 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">no more Christ-centered study </div><div class="t me60 x1e h69 y1ab5 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">than that! May its pursuit enable us </div><div class="t m270 x1e h69 yc5b ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to &quot;see Jesus, . . . crowned with </div><div class="t m26d x1e h69 y1b65 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">glory and honour&quot; (Heb. 2:9). </div><div class="t m497 x52 h69 y13fa ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In no sense is this only an </div><div class="t m6a6 x1e h69 y1fb0 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">academic study. A more spiritual </div><div class="t maa x1e h69 y1655 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(that is, related to the Spirit) and </div><div class="t mce5 x1e h69 y1e48 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">personal topic would be hard to </div><div class="t m91 x1e h69 y1d03 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">choose. If we wish, it will daily re-</div><div class="t mf95 x1e h69 y2013 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mind us to look up and see our In-</div><div class="t m604 x1e h69 y18cb ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tercessor ministering on our behalf </div><div class="t m21f x1e h69 y138e ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">before the Almighty, who ap-</div><div class="t mcb x1e h69 y641 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pointed Him to that merciful work. </div><div class="t me60 x1e h69 y1568 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Those who wish to refresh their </div><div class="t m842 x1e h69 y1c95 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">minds concerning this heavenly re-</div><div class="t m80e x1e h69 y1f5b ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ality can hardly do better than to </div><div class="t m558 x1e h69 yfa6 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">make the Epistle to the Hebrews </div><div class="t mfc x1e h69 y1b15 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their </div><div class="t m146f x1c h69 y1b16 ff5 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Furt